# My Lovely To-Do ✨📝

A soft & sweet to-do list app built with **React** and styled using **Tailwind CSS**. Cartoon vibes, pastel pink aesthetics, and a clean, minimal interface. Built with love 💖

---

## 🌟 Features

- ➕ Add tasks with a cute plus button
- 🗑️ Delete tasks with a trash icon
- ✏️ Edit tasks with a single click
- ✅ Mark tasks as completed (done tasks move to the bottom)
- 🔃 Filter by: All / Active / Done
- 💾 Auto-save tasks with **LocalStorage**
- 🎀 Minimal design with dashed notebook border
- 📱 Fully responsive and mobile-friendly

---

## 🚀 Getting Started

Clone the repository and install dependencies:

```bash
git clone https://github.com/Saeede-Azimipoor/My-Lovely-To-Do.git
cd My-Lovely-To-Do
npm install
npm start
```

App will start at `http://localhost:3000`

